cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.NA 

This paper deals with shape matching and metric space approximation, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also discusses the use of eigenfunctions and optimization, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper involves numerical methods for solving optimization problems, which falls under numerical analysis (cs.NA).
